article_title: Donald Trump Vows To 'Unsign' New Gun Laws President Obama Hasn't Even Announced Yet

article_metadata.description: A.M. Click: Donald Trump vows to 'unsign' the new gun legislation President Obama will sign this week, armed protesters won't leave an Oregon wildlife refuge and workers return to the site of the San Bernardino massacre.
